3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with automated learning of object categories. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible sub-category as the paper mentions the use of the proposed method for robotic applications. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible sub-category as the paper deals with 3D shape completion and alignment, which are relevant to computer graphics.
